{"word":"G3167 - μεγαλεῖος - megaleîos - meg-al-i'-os - Great things","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μεγαλεῖος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">megaleîos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">meg-al-i'-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Great things</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"மகிமையான, மகத்துவமான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"magnificent, excellent, splendid, wonderful"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3173 - μέγας - mégas - meg'-as/3173\">G3173</a>; <i>magnificent</i>, that is, (neuter plural as noun) a conspicuous <i>favor</i>, or (subjectively) <i>perfection:</i> - great things, wonderful works.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3167/3167\">G3167</a>, <a href=\"#/G3168/3168\">G3168</a>, <a href=\"#/G3169/3169\">G3169</a>, <a href=\"#/G3170/3170\">G3170</a>, <a href=\"#/G3171/3171\">G3171</a>, <a href=\"#/G3172/3172\">G3172</a>, <a href=\"#/G3173/3173\">G3173</a>, <a href=\"#/G3174/3174\">G3174</a>"}]}